text: Gatot Sudjito (28 October 1960 â€“ 18 January 2021) was an Indonesian politician. He was a member of the Golkar party. Sudjito was born in Sidoarjo Regency, Indonesia. From 2014 until his death, he was a member of the People's Representative Council. Sudjito died on 18 January 2021 in Malang, Indonesia from COVID-19, aged 60. ==References== Category:1960 births Category:2021 deaths Category:Indonesian politicians Category:Deaths from the COVID-19 pandemic in Indonesia
